As a user, I can upload recommendations

As a user, I can recommend specific fics to specifc users

As a user, I can sort and search fics

As a user, I can drop in a link to a fic and the 'new recommendations' form pulls in data and maps to the corresponding fields

As an admin, I can create new pages as new fandoms are added to the archive

As a user, Rec'd has a recommendation engine component that suggests fics for me

As a user, I can favorite the best of the best from Rec'd